"title": "5164: lips",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5164",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Lips as part of the human body</h2>\n<h3>As a vehicle of speech</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:13\">1SA 1:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:6\">JOB 15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:3\">JOB 33:3</a></p>\n<h3>As a means of eating and drinking</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:9\">SNG 7:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:3\">DAN 10:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:5\">JOL 1:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:29\">JHN 19:29</a></p>\n<h3>As an object of beauty</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:3\">SNG 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:11\">SNG 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:13\">SNG 5:13</a></p>\n<h2>Lips attributed to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:5\">JOB 11:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:12\">JOB 23:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:4\">PSA 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:34\">PSA 89:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:27\">ISA 30:27</a></p>\n<h2>Lips associated with various kinds of speech</h2>\n<h3>Praising lips</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:1\">PSA 34:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:15\">PSA 51:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:3\">PSA 63:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:5\">PSA 63:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:171\">PSA 119:171</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:19\">ISA 57:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:16\">MAT 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:2\">PSA 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:15\">HEB 13:15</a></p>\n<h3>Praying lips</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:2\">PSA 21:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:6\">JOB 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:1\">PSA 17:1</a></p>\n<h3>Lips that speak God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:7\">ACT 15:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:9\">EXO 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:22\">LUK 4:22</a></p>\n<h3>Lips that speak promises and vows</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:14\">PSA 66:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num30:6\">NUM 30:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num30:12\">NUM 30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:23\">DEU 23:23</a></p>\n<h3>Lips that give testimony</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:9\">PSA 40:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:13\">PSA 119:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:71\">LUK 22:71</a></p>\n<h3>Encouraging lips</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:5\">JOB 16:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:21\">PRO 10:21</a></p>\n<h2>Lips expressing different moods</h2>\n<h3>Joyful lips</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:21\">JOB 8:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:23\">PSA 71:23</a></p>\n<h3>Lips that express hesitancy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:12\">EXO 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:30\">EXO 6:30</a></p>\n<h3>Apprehensive lips</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:16\">HAB 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Lips that speak rashly</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:33\">PSA 106:33</a></p>\n<h2>Lips associated with wrong values</h2>\n<h3>Perverse and sinful lips</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:30\">JOB 6:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:12\">PSA 59:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:9\">PSA 140:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:24\">PRO 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:30\">PRO 16:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:1\">PRO 19:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>Lips can tempt into sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:3\">PRO 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:7\">PRO 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:4\">PRO 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:6-Prov18:7\">PRO 18:6–18:7</a></p>\n<h3>Deceitful lips</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:28\">PRO 24:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:18\">PSA 31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:13\">PSA 34:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps120:2\">PSA 120:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:18\">PRO 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:3\">ISA 59:3</a></p>\n<h3>Flattering lips</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:2-Ps12:3\">PSA 12:2–12:3</a></p>\n<h3>Hypocritical lips</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:16\">PSA 50:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:23-Prov26:24\">PRO 26:23–26:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:2\">JER 12:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:8\">MAT 15:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6\">MRK 7:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a></p>\n<h2>Lips associated with positive values</h2>\n<h3>Lips that speak truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:19\">PRO 12:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:6-Prov8:7\">PRO 8:6–8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:13\">PRO 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:16\">PRO 23:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:16\">JER 17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:6-Mal2:7\">MAL 2:6–2:7</a></p>\n<h3>Lips that speak wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:32\">PRO 10:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:9\">PSA 40:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:13\">PRO 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:7\">PRO 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:15\">PRO 20:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:17-Prov22:18\">PRO 22:17–22:18</a></p>\n<h2>Wise lips are profitable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:14\">PRO 12:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:2\">PRO 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:20\">PRO 18:20</a></p>\n<h2>Foolish lips are disastrous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:12\">ECC 10:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:3\">PRO 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:7\">PRO 18:7</a></p>\n<h2>Lips must be watched over by God</h2>\n<h3>People must guard their own lips</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:3\">PSA 141:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:13\">EXO 23:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:3\">PRO 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:10\">1PE 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:12\">PSA 34:12</a></p>\n<h3>Lips must be purified</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:7\">ISA 6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:17\">HOS 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:9\">ZEP 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:8\">COL 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Lips need God's touch</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:2\">PSA 45:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:16\">DAN 10:16</a></p>",
